list.name: Default
list.comment: Add Copyright notice to all files. Improve comments.

task.summary: Make the encrypt and decrypt method return char array and string respectively. Change state vector to char array.

Fix issue with CipherSaber2 implementation
Changed char arrays to byte arrays and it now works.
Removed feature where username was not displayed for same user twice in a row.
Update message encoding to conform with Protocol Ver 0.2

Updated method of reading bytes from socket
Updated method for reading bytes in from the socket to work with Bart's TauNet EchoServer.

Update method of sending bytes over socket.
Send messaged by writing bytes directly to socket. Works with Bart's TauNet EchoServer.
Store password as byte array, fix quit option 'q'

Don't print message alert
Don't print message alert if messages were received while user was typing. Print only the username and message for received messages.
Remove bool saving whether we were just waiting to receive a message.

Display username followed by message on the same line
Also add method to check if the message is from an unknown user.
Move Reply logic to its own method. Add message length checking.

Finished an untested version 0.1
All basic functionality is in place and working but untested.

Update to conform with revision 1 of TauNet protocol v0.2
Change receiver so 0 byte messages are discarded. Check if recipient is available before allowing user to compose a message to them.
